{"tid":2313341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] 川普係美國歷史上 第二位完全執政既共和黨總統","createTime":"2020-12-05T16:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T03:07:02.000Z","uid":52658,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ffce27bbdc41a49f2d6c02d5e91cd3b5e92b1b","tid":2313341,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq0Y8Hf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq0Y8Hf.png&h=f0a635d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ua6x8V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ua6x8V.png&h=d1f561fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ee7ArtW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fee7ArtW.png&h=44e610c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇返先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最強總統雷根都係跛腳鴨<br />\n1984年果年雷根係點做到橫掃525張人票<br />\n但眾議院唔過半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而小布希係第一任期4年都係取得參眾兩院<br />\n係共和黨第一次 亦都係最長時間既完全執政<br />\n跟住就係川普係2016-2018果2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過眾院係1954-1992年<br />\n長達接近40年時間由民主黨把持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f018adca10c1a57e0aaffcf2e5e6ebf8bf52c5c","tid":2313341,"uid":25468,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:49:52.000Z","msg":"香港係叫列根"},{"pid":"67be4d2ed577d1b6bfad511bedc704955f461b22","tid":2313341,"uid":25468,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"3f018adca10c1a57e0aaffcf2e5e6ebf8bf52c5c","tid":2313341,"uid":25468,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:49:52.000Z","msg":"香港係叫列根"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:50:07.000Z","msg":"仲有布殊"},{"pid":"479e0e8981be88aad5917c77968cc6a0847f4138","tid":2313341,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020